---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BackgroundShader from '../components/BackgroundShader.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="E-Cell VJIT | Community">
  <BackgroundShader />
  <Navbar />

  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-14 md:py-20 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 md:mb-14">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-200/80 mb-4">Under Construction</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-jakarta font-semibold tracking-tight mb-5">E-Cell Community</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 font-inter text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        This is the future E-Cell networking layer - a space for students, seniors, alumni, founders, and future mentors to stay connected even after college.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] gap-6 md:gap-8 items-stretch max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="glass noise-overlay rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-red-100">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-red-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          In progress
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-jakarta font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">A mini LinkedIn for the E-Cell ecosystem</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 font-inter text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          The idea is to give graduating seniors and founders a place to keep their E-Cell connections alive, discover people with similar goals, and stay visible to the college community.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 font-inter text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Each member would eventually have a public profile card with contact details, interests, startup stage, and the kind of support they are looking for - cofounders, mentors, users, collaborators, or speakers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 font-inter text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          That makes the community useful both during college and after graduation: a place to launch beta versions, find future speakers, and build a long-term alumni network around E-Cell.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <article class="glass noise-overlay rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-200/80 mb-4">What it will do</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 font-inter leading-relaxed">
            <p>• Let students discover seniors, alumni, and founders who are open to connecting.</p>
            <p>• Create public profile cards for networking, mentorship, and startup collaboration.</p>
            <p>• Make it easier to reconnect with E-Cell after graduation.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="glass noise-overlay rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-200/80 mb-4">Launch angle</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-inter leading-relaxed">
            This can be pitched as a resource for final-year students who want to keep building, find cofounders, reach mentors, or stay available for startup opportunities after B.Tech.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="glass noise-overlay rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-5">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-200/80 mb-2">Status</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-jakarta font-semibold tracking-tight">Community platform coming soon</h3>
        </div>
        <a href="/events" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-5 py-3 font-inter text-gray-100 transition-all hover:border-red-400/40 hover:bg-red-500/10 hover:text-white">
          Explore Events
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" width="16" height="16"></iconify-icon>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>